      <title>意大利联合信贷银行德国子公司因涉嫌 2 亿欧元增值税欺诈而遭突击搜查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/unicredit-german-unit-raided-in-200-million-vat-fraud-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧洲检察官突击搜查了慕尼黑联合信贷银行 (UniCredit) 的一个部门，以调查可能涉及 2 亿欧元（2.12 亿美元）的税务欺诈行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/unicredit-german-unit-raided-in-200-million-vat-fraud-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应担忧加剧，可可价格回升至每吨 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/cocoa-surges-back-to-10-000-a-ton-on-growing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球供应已经紧张，人们对西非产量下降的担忧加剧，可可期货价格攀升至近六个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/cocoa-surges-back-to-10-000-a-ton-on-growing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团因澳大利亚贸易失误损失逾 4,500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团因澳大利亚的一笔交易失误而蒙受的损失跃升至 7,000 多万澳元（4,500 万美元），这是近年来亚洲最大的大宗交易失误之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合健康保险公司枪击案引发健康保险公司的敌意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/unitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-dredges-up-hatred-of-health-insurers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团公司高管布莱恩·汤普森遭枪杀事件激起了美国人的强烈愤怒，他们认为医疗保险行业经常无法支付高额医疗费用并阻碍了人们获得必要的治疗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/unitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-dredges-up-hatred-of-health-insurers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 23:23:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员对就业报告倒计时持谨慎态度：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份重要的美国就业报告公布之前，市场基调谨慎，这份报告可能让交易员了解美联储的政策走向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 22:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦在史上最大规模海上风电招标中未收到任何投标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/denmark-receives-no-bids-in-largest-ever-offshore-wind-tender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦在其史上最大规模风电招标中未收到任何投标，这对欧洲推动可再生能源和削减化石燃料需求的努力是一个重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/denmark-receives-no-bids-in-largest-ever-offshore-wind-tender</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 16:56:26 GMT</pubDate>
